{
  "stem": "14251.3",
  "chunk_idx": 1,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.2,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Now, mind you, even in hiding they called each other Levent and Goldstein to each other, because you just don't first name people.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "Even in this intimate, crazy, dangerous circumstance, there were no first names used.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "And the agreement was, one night, I guess, he had told my father, if they should break in here-- this was in the dark- you three make a run for it, because it's really too late for us.",
      "word_count": 38
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "Forget the postal uniforms.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "Forget the roof.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "This is not going to work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 0,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "That was a dream four years ago that might work.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well, apparently, this was the moment that signaled to Levent it was time for his act.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't know what his act was going to be.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "His act was that he and his wife would pretend, in their small room without a door or a window, to get away.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Can you believe this?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 1,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Pretending to get away.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And one of them-- of the plainclothesmen shouted, it's Levent.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "He's trying to get away.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And so this one and the other one who was standing nearby-- two must have been in the back with them-- he must have made a scene enough that they thought he would escape them.",
      "word_count": 35
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Rushed through that door, that connecting door, to that area of the scuffle, and my father knew that was his signal.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And he pulled a key out of his pocket.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "He always had, apparently, this key on him.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Each had a key on him, in case of an emergency, to lock that door between.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And he locked that door between, in essence locking the Gestapo in with the two Levents.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 2,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And we-- out through the hole.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
